'Qantas has worked with the ATSB to investigate a weight and balance anomaly on a Canberra to Perth flight,' a Qantas spokesperson told Daily Mail Australia.

'The investigation found that due to an administrative error, the weight of some passengers was incorrectly recorded as adults rather than children.'

